{"tid":2450802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"多名作家翻譯戈曼詩作被拒用 原因竟係「唔係黑人又唔係女性」 質疑用人睇背景唔睇才能","createTime":"2021-03-17T16:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T21:30:38.000Z","uid":63183,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"07f83f6c6d41453d82b2d538bfe988048c65e94e","tid":2450802,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T16:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B-2.png?w=1200&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259C%258B-2.png%3Fw%3D1200%26ssl%3D1&h=6d8677e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汁：<a href=\"https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5858\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F5858&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT%2F3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=f4355505\" target=\"_blank\">https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5858</a><br />\n美國青年詩人戈曼（Amanda Gorman）喺拜登朗讀詩作，一躍成名，世界各地都要翻譯佢嘅作品。但係加泰羅尼亞嘅翻譯作家域陀&middot;奧比奧斯（Victor Obiols）就話，本來出版社應承咗畀佢做翻譯，但人哋就話佢知因為佢冇非裔血統，又唔係年輕女性，佢嘅翻譯工作就要取消。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/storage.googleapis.com/afs-prod/media/94e6a95a8e5a4ef1b66bf6df115994d1/3000.jpeg?resize=3000%2C2000&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Fafs-prod%2Fmedia%2F94e6a95a8e5a4ef1b66bf6df115994d1%2F3000.jpeg%3Fresize%3D3000%252C2000%26ssl%3D1&h=783ebdfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n域陀接受法新社訪問嗰時講：「佢哋話，我唔適合做呢次翻譯。佢哋冇質疑我嘅翻譯能力，但佢哋要搵個背景唔同嘅人，最好係女性、後生、激進主義者，最好係黑人添。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.culturascf.cat/img/image/fotos/victorobiols.jpg?resize=1200%2C800&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.culturascf.cat%2Fimg%2Fimage%2Ffotos%2Fvictorobiols.jpg%3Fresize%3D1200%252C800%26ssl%3D1&h=aeeba978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加泰隆尼亞作家域陀（Victor Obiols）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n域陀做過好多經典嘅英文譯加泰文作品，例如莎士比亞、王爾德呢啲大作。佢喺三個禮拜前收到巴塞隆拿出版商Univers嘅要求，將戈曼嘅詩譯做加泰文。佢做完之後，出版社就收到一個訊息，指責佢係唔適合嘅人。域陀唔肯定係嚟自原本嘅發行商定係戈曼嘅經理人。<br />\n<br />\n身為巴塞隆拿居民嘅域陀話：「呢個問題好複雜，好難三言兩語講得清。但係，如果因為詩人係21歲嘅美國人，我就譯唔到佢嘅詩嘅話，不如話我唔係公元前八世紀嘅希臘人，所以譯唔到荷馬；或者唔係16世紀嘅英國人，所以譯唔到莎士比亞。」<br />\n<br />\n出版社Univers就冇回應。域陀就話，即使係咁，出版社都應承會為佢嘅翻譯作品畀錢。<br />\n<br />\n無獨有偶，2020年布克國際獎得主、29歲荷蘭作家盧卡斯（Marieke Lucas）早前都獲邀將戈曼詩作譯成荷蘭語，惹來批評。有人質疑盧卡斯係白人，又冇相關經驗，盧卡斯就退出唔做呢單翻譯喇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/40C4/production/_117508561_gettyimages-1228213925.jpg?resize=976%2C549&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F976%2Fcpsprodpb%2F40C4%2Fproduction%2F_117508561_gettyimages-1228213925.jpg%3Fresize%3D976%252C549%26ssl%3D1&h=f087dca8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荷蘭作家盧卡斯（Marieke Lucas）<br />\n<br />\n不過，盧卡斯用荷蘭文就寫咗首詩「乜都可以居住」（Everything Inhabitable）回應對佢嘅批評，亦都被翻譯做多種語言登喺報紙。"},{"pid":"a9c93ed4d03953482474586271f4a09d84ec23c8","tid":2450802,"uid":60814,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T16:04:07.000Z","msg":"個黑妹詩人紅係因為佢黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f406d48d58426d94b859611cf4e975029898883","tid":2450802,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T16:05:43.000Z","msg":"咁都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9adafc18f66b5358397ae4b610074bd7954a75d8","tid":2450802,"uid":53248,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T16:06:12.000Z","msg":"d垃圾偽文青寫d懶感性既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad329912d96a95da5d6e4dfab42c343b992172d","tid":2450802,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T16:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dru