"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T16:38:17.000Z","msg":"只有同性戀跨性別多重性別認同環保動保素食社會主義黑人女肥婆先有資格接受呢個偉大既工作<br />\n白皮豬可以收皮"},{"pid":"a6e05c55cd5c3b00cd7ec6c6422eed22f20ed699","tid":2450802,"uid":390224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T16:43:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只有同性戀跨性別多重性別認同環保動保素食社會主義黑人女<span class=\"red\"><strong>肥婆</strong></span>先有資格接受呢個偉大既工作<br />\n白皮豬可以收皮</blockquote><br />\n請不要物化女性，係horizontally challenged<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06155304dd3ff23ce8a5876b4127401faf5facd1","tid":2450802,"uid":349494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T21:30:38.000Z","msg":"梅根二世"}]}